Package model

Class BibliographicProduct

java.lang.Object
model.BibliographicProduct
Direct Known Subclasses:
Book, Magazine
public class BibliographicProduct extends Object
The BibliographicProduct class represents a bibliographic product in the virtual library system. It serves as the base class for specific types of bibliographic products such as books and magazines.
